<i>what I used to have.</i>

280
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,279
<i>Juan,</i>

281
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,464
<i>you know what?</i>

282
00:24:23,759 --> 00:24:25,559
<i>The happiest thing</i>

283
00:24:25,559 --> 00:24:26,960
<i>in the world</i>

284
00:24:28,279 --> 00:24:29,839
