285
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,720
<i>Go ahead.</i>

286
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:34,559
<i>Fully express your passion</i>

287
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:37,000
<i>and unleash your brilliance.</i>

288
00:24:38,599 --> 00:24:39,680
<i>Besides,</i>

289
00:24:40,799 --> 00:24:43,039
