326
00:29:19,559 --> 00:29:21,279
I felt as long as I guarded the shop,

327
00:29:23,599 --> 00:29:24,768
I could keep

328
00:29:27,599 --> 00:29:28,680
my uncle.

329
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,279
