353
00:31:09,319 --> 00:31:10,336
No.

354
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,559
So are you going to give me a personal tour?

355
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:16,800
Sure.

356
00:31:18,079 --> 00:31:19,104
Let's go.

357
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,504
I didn't expect

358
00:31:33,504 --> 00:31:35,039
